comment: Accelerated Networking on Azure exposes a new SRIOV interface to the VM.
This interface is transparently bonded to the synthetic interface,
so NetworkManager should just ignore any SRIOV interfaces.

config.cmdline: ro crashkernel=auto console=tty1 console=ttyS0 earlyprintk=ttyS0 rootdelay=300 scsi_mod.use_blk_mq=y
